China is ambitious, aiming to get 300 million people involved with winter sports. What is the significance of Beijing 2022 in the context of the global pandemic? Kyrgyz President Sadyr Zhaparov said Beijing 2022 will write a new chapter in the history of the Winter Olympics in terms of content, size and splendor. Under the guidance of the Olympic spirit, uniting the world and promoting a healthy and active lifestyle, Beijing 2022 is of great significance.